   }
   ```
   This modification changes the condition to `-i < n`. For `i = 0`, `-i = 0`, and the loop will execute when `i` is decremented to `-1`, `-2`, `-3`, and so on. The loop will run indefinitely.

4. Replace "i < n" with "i + n":
   ```c++
